\subsection{Cell size and carbon quotas of phytoplankton populations}

Cell diameter ($\mu$m) is estimated by a Mie-based model with parameters calculated from phytoplankton cultures using the medium index of refraction. (Fig. \ref{fig:Mie}).  The plots below show time series and maps of the average diameter for each population (Fig. \ref{fig:phyP_diam}).

